y, fire pet, etc.  There really isn't a good or bad pet, some are more troublesome and pop more than others, but they all do the same thing, attack until death or until told not too.  Besides that, spells, yakety schmackety, same ole stuff.  Summons, heh, those are REAL fun, and you save money, your hungry, make food, thirsty, make water, (wish you could make redwine), but that's another story *swig*.  Anyways, play hard, make friends, level, camp, do everything in eq that you can (cept for kill Captain N'Farre, my personal hero, who is, the man) And who knows, I might make another post (super huge) on every class, race, goodpoints and bad about them, etc.  Hell, why not now.  HAHAHAHAHAHA.<br><br>Good fight, Good night.<br><br>Dashiatis<br><br>Bristlebane<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
