	   <tr><td colspan=2>Yes, it is possible to get level 17 pets at level 16. For some wierd reason they jump back up to being able to con yellow at 16. At 20 you can get white cons, but 95% of the time you will get blues. After level 20 all pets that you summon will be blue or green. The only exception to this is the magician epic pet. However, since it is nearly impossible to get, you will prolly be in your high 50's/level 60 by the time you get it, and then it would con blue.<br><br>One of the previous posters said that the focus items don't work on pets until level 34. That is untrue. They work on all pets under level 49. My first mage was in his 40's before the focus items even came out, so that sort of sucked, but the last magician I made had all of his focus items but the fire one at level 16, and they DO make pets that are under level 34 more powerful.<br><br>Former Addict of Everquest.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
