	   <tr><td colspan=2>I mainly agree with this guy. It is very true that in many places the earth pet simply sucks. Too many magicians stick to just using the earth pet. I DEFINATELY agree with part about the fire pet. It is SOOO good in lots of situations. Also, the air pet becomes very good once you get to about 24. It gets better and better as a tank as you level, and its stun gets better and better. Yes, it does dish out the least amount of damage overall, but it still does good damage.<br><br>Former Addict of Everquest.<br><br>Just remember everyone, Everquest is an awesome game. When you are playing it, continually think of how lucky you are. Everquest has left me so many good memories, and I am continually thankful that I was able to be a part of the game for the time that I played (nearly 2 years). Cherish every second that you play it, and try not to get to caught up in leveling and powergaming. It will frustrate you many times and you will got angry at it, but always remember how lucky you are to get to experience something so awesome as Everquest.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
